name: IGNORAMUS
description:
THE WORLD IS FINE! ALL IS FUCKING WELL! WE'RE LIVING IN GOOD TIMES!

Our existence is shared among those who are not from the same fabric of reality. A world where facts are denied for the sake of having an opinion. Or that the death of innocent millions and losing a few quarters are synonymous in terms of being necessary collateral damage. The world is on fire, ignorance its gasoline and denial being the lit match. 

I see six. You see nine. Some see a fucking butterfly.
